#ğŸ• Food Delivery Time Prediction Using Machine Learning

##ğŸ¯ Project Objective
This project predicts food delivery time (in minutes) using machine learning by analysing factors such as distance, traffic, weather conditions, and delivery partner details.
Goal: Improve ETA accuracy for platforms like Zomato, Swiggy, UberEats.

##ğŸ“‚ Dataset Information
The dataset contains detailed records of food deliveries, including:
Delivery partner information
Restaurant and customer locations 
Traffic and weather conditions
Type of order and vehicle
Number of deliveries in a trip
Time-related features (hour, day, peak hour, festival status)
Actual delivery time (target)

